is recipe can be replaced with <em>Yoghurt and jalapeño dressing<\/em>.","If cooking for one, use any leftover beef in a sandwich or wrap the next day.  Leftover salsa can be served as a dip or tossed through a rice or pasta salad.","Store leftover Mexican spice mix in an airtight container to use in other dishes.","Corn tortillas are not always gluten free, as some use a combination of wheat and corn to create a softer end result.  Select certified gluten free corn tortillas to make this a gluten free recipe.","You can make your own tortillas in the Thermomix.  Visit the online Recipe Community (recipecommunity.com.au) for free tortilla recipes."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","1h 30m","2 portions"]}